highlights.text: “Break” by Misha Omar is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 25 spots at #62.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “Kokki” is the highest at #15.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 138 days straight.
“The Subway” by Chappell Roan is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #8.
